'''明尼阿波利斯美術館'''（{{lang-en|Minneapolis Institute of Art}}）<ref name="MPRname">{{Cite web|title=MIA reboots brand to become 'Mia'|url=http://www.mprnews.org/story/2015/08/10/feldman-art-museum|accessdate=2015-12-27|date=2015-08-10|publisher=Minnesota Public Radio News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045118/http://www.mprnews.org/story/2015/08/10/feldman-art-museum|archivedate=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WhatsIn">{{Cite web|title=Once at Mia: What's in a name? — Minneapolis Institute of Art|url=http://new.artsmia.org/stories/once-at-mia-whats-in-a-name-2/|accessdate=2015-12-27|publisher=Minneapolis Institute of Art|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101095519/http://new.artsmia.org/stories/once-at-mia-whats-in-a-name-2/|archivedate=2015-11-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>是位於[[美國|美國]][[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]][[明尼阿波利斯|明尼阿波利斯]]的一座美術館。

==历史==
1883年建立，美術館的面積達32000平方米，藏品約八萬件<ref name="100k">{{Cite web|title=William M. Griswold Appointed New Director of the Minneapolis Institute of Arts|url=https://new.artsmia.org/press/william-m-griswold-appointed-new-director-of-the-minneapolis-institute-of-arts/|accessdate=10 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614041216/https://new.artsmia.org/press/william-m-griswold-appointed-new-director-of-the-minneapolis-institute-of-arts/|archivedate=2020-06-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref> ，常設展可免費參觀（特展收費），是美國中西部北部地區規模最大的美術館<ref>{{cite web|title=Minneapolis Institute of Arts|url=http://www.artsmia.org/index.php?section_id=7|access-date=2015-12-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101163334/http://www.artsmia.org/index.php?section_id=7|archivedate=2013-11-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

